! This file contains mapping from abbreviations and some acronyms to full
! forms for e.g. text-to-speech purposes. This is a supplement to the analyser;
! the analyser must tag the strings as +ABBR or similar for the transcriptions
! to work.

! ========================================================================== !
! !!            !!!North Sami abbreviations                               !
! ========================================================================== !

!! We describe here how abbreviations in North Sami are read out, e.g.
!! for text-to-speech systems.

LEXICON Root

